                        Each return is prepared with careful review of income, expenses, payroll,
                        and supporting documentation. We ensure compliance with federal and state
                        regulations while identifying allowable deductions and credits.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our methodical approach supports accurate filings, audit readiness,
                        and smoother financial planning throughout the year.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 2 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-header">Individual Income Tax Returns</button>
                <div class="accordion-content">
