                        This includes self-employment income, rental properties, investment activity,
                        retirement income, and other taxable events.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our focus is accuracy, compliance, and minimizing errors that can lead to
                        delays, notices, or penalties.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 3 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-header">Real Estate Tax Services</button>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>
                        We work closely with landlords and real estate investors to ensure proper reporting
                        and strategic planning.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Rental income and expense reporting</li>
                        <li>Depreciation and cost recovery</li>
                        <li>Capital gains planning</li>
                        <li>1031 exchange guidance</li>
                        <li>Long-term real estate tax planning</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Whether you own one property or multiple investments, we help you
                        understand the tax impact and remain compliant.
                    </p>
                </div>
